### 8. Admin Overview "Quick Actions" — Wrong Icon for Announcements
**File:** [AdminOverview.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/admin/AdminOverview.tsx#L93-94)

Both "New Announcement" and "Review Admissions" use `ClipboardList` icon. Announcements should use `Megaphone`.

---

### 9. Admin Students Modal — `classId` Not Reset on Modal Close
**File:** [AdminStudents.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/admin/AdminStudents.tsx)

When the modal closes (Cancel or submit success), `classId` is not reset to `classData[0].id`. If the user opens the modal a second time, the dropdown may be blank.

---

### 10. Hero Section — Images May 404
**File:** [HeroSection.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/components/sections/HeroSection.tsx#L6-12)

The hero uses local images: `/images/Home/flag.png`, `/images/Home/1.jpg`, etc. If any of these files don't exist in `/public/images/`, the hero carousel will show broken images with no fallback. There's no `onError` handler.

---

### 11. Google Maps Embed — Invalid Placeholder URL
**File:** [Contact.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/Contact.tsx#L90)

The iframe `src` contains a fake placeholder embed URL (with `5f5f5f5f5f5f5f5f` in it). This will show an error in the map. Needs a real Google Maps embed URL for Migori, Kenya.

---

### 12. Parent Portal — No Real Data Connection
**Files:** `src/pages/parent/ParentOverview.tsx`, `ParentChild.tsx`, `ParentResults.tsx`, etc.

These pages are likely still using static/mock data and are not connected to the `db` layer. Parents won't see real data about their children.

---

### 13. Student & Teacher Portals — Not Connected to DB
**Files:** `src/pages/student/`, `src/pages/teacher/`

Same issue as #12. Assignments, results, timetable pages are likely still using mockup arrays and not `db.assignments.list()` etc.

