## 🟢 Minor/Polish Issues

### 14. Announcements Page — `created_by` Field Not Set on Create
**File:** [AdminAnnouncements.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/admin/AdminAnnouncements.tsx)

`db.announcements.create()` is called without passing `created_by`. The logged-in admin's user ID should be included.

### 15. Admissions Form — No Phone Format Validation
**File:** [Admissions.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/Admissions.tsx)

Phone number input accepts any text. Should add `pattern` attribute for basic Kenyan phone number validation (e.g. `+254...`).

### 16. `siteInfo.phone` Is a Placeholder
**File:** [data.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/lib/data.ts#L8)

`phone: '+254 700 000 000'` is clearly a placeholder. Should be updated to the real school number before going live.

### 17. Portal Sidebar — No Active State for Sub-paths
**File:** [PortalLayout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/components/portal/PortalLayout.tsx#L148)

```tsx
const active = location.pathname === item.href
```

Uses exact match. If a future page has a child route like `/admin/students/123`, the "Students" sidebar item won't highlight. Should use `location.pathname.startsWith(item.href)` (with `/admin` being the exact match exception).

### 18. `Admissions` Catch Block Still Uses Named `e`
**File:** [Admissions.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/BFA/src/pages/Admissions.tsx#L64)

Minor lint consistency — same `catch (e: any)` pattern that was already fixed in other files.

